title: Google\Cloud\Bigtable\Admin\V2\Table
name: Table
description:
A collection of user data indexed by row, column, and timestamp.

Each table is served using the resources of its parent cluster.

Generated from protobuf message google.bigtable.admin.v2.Table

Extends \Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

methods.name: getName
methods.description:
(OutputOnly) The unique name of the table. Values are of the form projects/<project>/instances/<instance>/tables/[_a-zA-Z0-9][-_.a-zA-Z0-9]*.

Views: NAME_ONLY, SCHEMA_VIEW, REPLICATION_VIEW, FULL

methods.description:
